<html><head><meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8"/></head><body>
<p>Hi {{{Contact.FirstName}}},</p>
<p>This is the last note from me on this. I’ve reached out a few times about Atrium and don’t want to keep showing up in your inbox if there’s nothing here for you.</p>
<p>Three possibilities:</p>
<ol>
<li><em>Wrong time.</em> Reply with a date and I’ll circle back then.</li>
<li><em>Interested but slammed.</em> Reply “yes” and I’ll send a 15-minute calendar link.</li>
<li><em>Not for me.</em> Reply “no” and I close the file. No follow-up.</li>
</ol>
<p>Wishing you all the best.</p>
<p>Thank You,</p>
</body></html>
